


Kong Konnect:
  a SaaS based platform,  provides Kong hosted Control Planes and Data Plane nodes.
  Dataplane nodes can run either on-premise or cloud-hosted environments, or fully managed by Kong Konnect with Dedicated Cloud Gateways.

Kong Ingress Controller(KIC):
  It allows you to run Kong Gateway as a Kubernetes Ingress, i.e., accepts traﬃc from outside the Kubernetes platform, and load balances it to services running inside the platform.
  KIC receives k8s CRD manifests directed to Kong Gateway and translates these into Kong conﬁguration and applies it to Kong Gateway.

